Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:12.14,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}豹のように美しいくわたし
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.50,0:00:18.14,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}着飾るは闇の毛皮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:24.18,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}谷間の百合　踏みつけても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.49,0:00:29.80,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}あなたの場所に向かうため
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:35.99,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}牙を立てる果肉の甘さは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:42.25,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}結ばぬ実の不実の夢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.44,0:00:44.81,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}交わりましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.01,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}逃げてるのか追ってるのか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:50.73,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}わからなくなるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.10,0:00:54.14,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}わたしを視て　もっと深く
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:57.07,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}溺れ乱れ蜜地獄
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.21,0:01:00.00,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}魔触の爪　腐蝕の骨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.21,0:01:02.70,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}軋む音響かせ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:06.15,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}これが愛か憎しみなのか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:09.07,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}答えは必要ですか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.27,0:01:14.69,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}ああ捕まれた心臓は
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.89,0:01:21.04,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}あなたの氷のような
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.32,0:01:27.47,OP日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)\be1}指の中で生き返るわ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:12.14,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}如同豹一般美丽无比的我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.50,0:00:18.14,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}装扮在身的是黑暗的毛皮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.52,0:00:24.18,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}即使不惜践踏过山涧的百合
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.49,0:00:29.80,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}也是为了前往你的所在之处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:35.99,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}能让人倒牙般甘甜鲜美的果肉是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.22,0:00:42.25,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}未成熟果实的不真实的梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.44,0:00:44.81,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}混杂在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.11,0:00:48.01,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}是否要逃避呢　抑或去追赶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:50.73,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}连我自己都还不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.10,0:00:54.14,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}请注视着我吧　更加深邃一点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.38,0:00:57.07,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}便沉溺混乱于甜蜜地狱中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.21,0:01:00.00,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}魑魅魍魉之爪　腐蚀了的骸骨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.21,0:01:02.70,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}吱嘎摇曳之声在回响
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:06.15,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}这究竟是爱呢　抑或会是憎恨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.36,0:01:09.07,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}还有必要回答这个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.27,0:01:14.69,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}啊　那颗被揪住的心脏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.89,0:01:21.04,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}在你的那极度冰冷无比的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.32,0:01:27.47,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1000)\be1}手指中再一次起死而回生了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.87,0:22:24.15,ED日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}光を…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.47,0:22:36.89,ED日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}舞い散る花の香りは甘く囁く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.02,0:22:47.53,ED日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}繰り返される終わりのない綻びは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:56.04,ED日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}小さな傷跡さえ　癒せない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.23,0:23:01.42,ED日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}悲しみの輪　重ねて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.57,0:23:04.84,ED日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}あなたの手　あなたの声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.06,0:23:11.21,ED日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}あなたの面影を　求めても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.15,0:23:15.56,ED日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}遠い　ドアは　開くことなく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:21.93,ED日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}問いかけた命の意味　空しくあの空に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.05,0:23:28.64,ED日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}木霊して　響くだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.68,0:23:33.30,ED日文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}永遠の夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.87,0:22:24.15,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}光芒啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.47,0:22:36.89,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}飞落的花朵散发出淡淡的幽香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.02,0:22:47.53,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}一直反复着　永无终结地绽放着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:56.04,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}即使是小小的伤痕　也不能得到治愈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.23,0:23:01.42,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}悲伤之轮　再度旋转
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.67,0:23:04.84,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}即使渴望着你的手　你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.06,0:23:11.21,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}甚至是你的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.15,0:23:15.56,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}也仍旧无法打开远处的那扇门
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.77,0:23:21.93,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}向那片空虚的天空　追寻生命的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.05,0:23:28.64,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}回响起的只是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.68,0:23:33.30,ED中文,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\be1}名为「永远」的梦境
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.80,0:01:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水银灯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.42,0:01:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是蔷薇少女的第一人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.31,0:01:53.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水银灯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起来吗  呐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:01:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:02:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人他不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.60,0:02:03.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  你能站起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.47,0:02:09.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  真的是蔷薇少女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:24.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22\fsp160}　{\fsp1}Rosa Mystica\N{\r}你从父亲大人那里得到蔷薇圣母了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.04,0:02:26.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人  父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.13,0:02:31.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.07,0:02:36.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人  父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.69,0:02:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一上来就展开攻击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:50.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水银灯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.74,0:02:56.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你真的是第一人偶  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水银灯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.36,0:03:16.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  蔷薇少女第一人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.85,0:03:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.97,0:03:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长得可真漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别碰她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:33.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我叫莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.03,0:03:36.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是哪里不舒服？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.21,0:03:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  真红  她会不会有些怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.15,0:03:50.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶中也不乏内向的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.35,0:03:53.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但总感觉有些别扭  雪白雪白的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.56,0:03:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就要解决掉她了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:02.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.23,0:04:11.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在寻找父亲之前还有你必须要做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:15.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.23,0:04:34.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活人偶？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  似乎有个男人为了寻找她们而来到了这个城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且他还说会给协助寻找的人一定的报酬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:45.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一定又是哪个王公贵族的消遣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:48.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.06,0:04:51.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！  全洒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.71,0:04:54.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:00.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.84,0:05:01.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右  左
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:07.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.84,0:05:10.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样  你能办得到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.16,0:05:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.53,0:05:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.49,0:05:16.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.39,0:05:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:26.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要对水银灯那么好？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么不行吗？！  她也是蔷薇少女不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是必须要打倒她才行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.96,0:05:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你却每天都在帮助她练习走路  没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.71,0:05:42.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莎拉  那个人偶很乖哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:44.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什么嘛  突然说这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.67,0:05:49.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:50.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  非常的优美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人会不会为此而高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:06:58.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.91,0:06:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:00.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会对我微笑吗  会拥抱我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.77,0:07:05.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.64,0:07:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有假吧  绝对？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.99,0:07:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然不假  因为你的确如此美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想让父亲大人早点见到…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.50,0:07:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见到我…  行走的样子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.89,0:07:25.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你  真红  多亏了你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:28.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这都是你自己努力的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…  这份感激我该如何表达
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  真的谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.71,0:07:46.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再练习一会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.51,0:07:48.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.07,0:08:03.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上哪会有活人偶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.76,0:08:04.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:08.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  这戒指可真美丽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.65,0:08:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别…别碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.74,0:08:15.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一声不吭就触碰女士  真是失礼！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:17.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诚然  真是抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:23.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么在道歉之余  我能拜见一下您的闺房吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拒绝！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:27.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真遗憾  打扰你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:30.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎并不在这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.22,0:08:35.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:39.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后  那个男人就回去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不过他是怎么知道的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.84,0:08:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可对谁都没说过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.89,0:08:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕  是人偶师…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:49.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人偶师？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:08:57.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.45,0:08:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.23,0:09:02.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  一定是梦…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:04.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了个奇怪的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.77,0:09:10.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被丢弃了  然后看到你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被父亲拥抱着的你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.81,0:09:15.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:22.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦  那只是你做的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.06,0:09:34.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  准备吃早餐吧  莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.42,0:09:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的记忆正在逐渐恢复…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.70,0:09:49.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外  人偶师也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Lempicka\N{\r}琅碧卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:59.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  正好来做个了断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.47,0:10:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.76,0:10:03.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.57,0:10:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去战斗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.92,0:10:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很奇怪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.40,0:10:12.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在爱丽丝游戏中  如果不打倒所有的人就无法见到父亲大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.13,0:10:17.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使你战胜了苍星石  但若仍这样留着水银灯那还有什么意义呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.54,0:10:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不该说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.88,0:10:21.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.54,0:10:24.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请好好待她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:27.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:34.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱丽丝游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:54.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是顶惹人厌的帽子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:57.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我从父亲大人那里得到的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:58.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.90,0:11:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红  你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.42,0:11:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会在战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:09.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.47,0:11:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然能够进入我的n之领域…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了  别伤害真红
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫水银灯  是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:22.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  似乎通过镜子来到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.38,0:11:26.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我是水银灯  是蔷薇少女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:29.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇少女…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.51,0:11:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  蔷薇少女第一人偶水银灯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:36.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是第一…？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.22,0:11:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.07,0:11:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快退下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:39.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:41.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话  退下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:45.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是爱丽丝游戏？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.58,0:11:47.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…  全听到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.23,0:11:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然知情也就不必多费口舌了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  苍星石
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.66,0:11:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.46,0:12:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内部…  是空的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.34,0:12:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是蔷薇少女
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.58,0:12:27.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是未完成的人偶半成品
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.90,0:12:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是仅凭着对父亲的思念而行动的可怜的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.55,0:12:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不拥有蔷薇圣母  总有一天会消失的人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:40.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…  那不是真的  不是真的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.12,0:12:42.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是蔷薇少女！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:45.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人制作的  第一人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.77,0:12:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不去莎拉那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了能让你作为人偶幸福地生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.73,0:12:58.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了那么多的努力…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.63,0:12:59.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你不来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.35,0:13:03.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能作为人偶和莎拉一起过着幸福的生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.87,0:13:09.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…  已经死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.98,0:13:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:13.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:15.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红！  救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.25,0:13:22.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红！ 真红！ 救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.49,0:13:26.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不在最初告诉她事情的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.76,0:13:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么说得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.09,0:13:43.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能对她说「你是见不到父亲的」吗？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.39,0:13:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得那样总比说谎要好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:14:01.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…  不是蔷薇少女…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.00,0:14:03.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是个半成品…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:08.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人  为什么会创造出我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:11.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会创造出这样的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.82,0:14:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是因为爱着我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.73,0:14:19.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我究竟是为何而生…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:05.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  苍星石也赶快…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我还没与真红…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:11.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再给媒介增加负担了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.98,0:15:13.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:14.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:19.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.41,0:15:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石和苍星石都…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:26.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了  莎拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.37,0:15:29.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要成为一个出色的淑女哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.02,0:16:05.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.71,0:16:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.29,0:16:13.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很吃惊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.74,0:16:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定很吃惊呢  因为明明发生了那种事还…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:21.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.03,0:16:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  果然是蔷薇少女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.96,0:16:27.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人认同了我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.11,0:16:28.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.36,0:16:32.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇圣母就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:35.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事  怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.74,0:16:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我能够挺起胸膛说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「我是水银灯  蔷薇少女第一人偶」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多关照  真红
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.99,0:16:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人  你怎么会是蔷薇少女…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.35,0:16:55.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:56.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.34,0:17:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  你还未完成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.13,0:17:03.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还只是可怜的人偶半成品…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:09.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇少女  是以究极的少女爱丽丝为目标制作出来的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.03,0:17:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…  和我们不同…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.56,0:17:18.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.31,0:17:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.29,0:17:23.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直是用这种眼光来看待我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为我是比你劣等的可怜人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.67,0:17:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我的温柔话语以及援助之手  都只是在可怜我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:38.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是为了让自己高高在上的优越感得以满足
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.29,0:17:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.92,0:17:49.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是想要一边让自己更为高贵更为父亲所宠爱  一边嘲弄着我  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那样的  不是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.86,0:17:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:54.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗嗦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.66,0:17:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个讨厌的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.80,0:18:03.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是被生的有点得天独厚而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.46,0:18:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是偶尔被制作得还不错而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:13.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说  我的存在只是为了用来提高你自身的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.61,0:18:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的！  我只是希望至少能让你和莎拉一起幸福地生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.85,0:18:21.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这不正是在玩弄我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.80,0:18:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有认同我是蔷薇少女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样的人偶没可能成为爱丽丝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.44,0:18:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为爱丽丝的  将会是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比任何人都深爱着父亲大人的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将会成为爱丽丝  接受父亲大人的拥抱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接受父亲大人的关怀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.71,0:19:16.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有你才会得到的父亲的宠爱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还给我！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:23.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥抱着你  注视着你  父亲大人深爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的这些幻想…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:30.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我来打破吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.02,0:19:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲大人深爱着的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:38.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正深爱着的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.72,0:19:40.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:03.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是从父亲大人那里得到的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.50,0:20:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充满着父亲大人的思念…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈…哈哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.68,0:20:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为…什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…明明是个废物
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.42,0:20:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.55,0:20:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半成品…废物！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.53,0:20:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,废物！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.38,0:20:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.83,0:20:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡事都有终结之时
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.61,0:20:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉普拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:21:01.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翠星石和苍星石  都已入眠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.27,0:21:03.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红也已解除契约
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:06.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时代的爱丽丝游戏已然结束
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.60,0:21:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待将留给下一个时代
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.84,0:21:11.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:17.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真红！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.29,0:21:28.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以那个胸针…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.78,0:21:31.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.53,0:21:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.30,0:21:51.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.77,0:22:00.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冥冥
